aa(lp376
VSo the question I'd like to leave you with, really,
p377
aVis \u2014 for all aspects of the things that your community needs
p378
aVin order to thrive,
p379
aVhow can it be done in such a way
p380
aVthat drastically reduces its carbon emissions,
p381
aVwhile also building resilience?
